summary: A simple free player home - in the form of a Khajiit tent - near Whitewatch Tower, just northeast of Whiterun.
descriptionHtml:
[size=4][b][b][i][color=#ffff00]Skyrim SE version nowÂ [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/2987]available[/url][/color][/i][/b]

[u]Description[/u][/b][/size]
A simple free player home - in the form of a Khajiit tent - near Whitewatch Tower, just northeast of Whiterun.

Has a bed, table w/chair, several player-owned non-respawning containers, cooking pot, some firewood, wood chopping block, and a tanning rack.

[size=4][b][u]Versions[/u][/b][/size]
See "Latest Version" link above.

[size=4][b][u]Installation[/u][/b][/size]
Download with NMM. Activate in NMM.

[size=4][b][u]Removal[/u][/b][/size]
Deactivate in NMM.

[size=4][b][u]Compatibility[/u][/b][/size]
No known issues, but will likely conflict with anything which mods the same cell.
